      </div>

      <div class="info-tip">
        <strong>How it works:</strong> Build IF/THEN rules using price data. The engine checks each candle in the historical data and counts how many times your pattern occurs.
      </div>

      <div class="preset-patterns" style="margin-top:16px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:12px;">
        <div style="font-size:0.72em;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;">⚡ Preset Patterns</div>
        <button class="preset-btn" data-preset="dip3">3-day dip → bounce on day 4</button>
        <button class="preset-btn" data-preset="pump3">3-day pump → dump on day 4</button>
        <button class="preset-btn" data-preset="aboveSMA">Close above 50-SMA → next day</button>
        <button class="preset-btn" data-preset="volumeSpike">Volume spike 2x avg → next close</button>
        <button class="preset-btn" data-preset="breakout">Break above 20-day high → continuation</button>
